modules.description: Provides functions to manage and execute build processes, including initializing a development environment and triggering builds. Operates with system paths, configuration settings, and build artifacts. Used to set up isolated project environments and automate the build workflow.

Converts Markdown text to HTML, with and without table of contents, and handles file content with metadata pairs. Processes input as strings or metadata-content pairs, returning HTML output or structured results. Supports generating HTML documents alongside extracted tables of contents for organized content rendering.
